sigkdd#Hotel: The hotel is the child of the conferencehall.
sigkdd#Place: The main office is the parent of the hotel and the conferencehall.
sigkdd#Abstract: Abstract is a child of document which is parented by paper.
sigkdd#Document: The document review is the parent of the paper and the abstract.
sigkdd#Deadline_Abstract_Submission: The deadline for abstract submission is the parent of the deadline for paper submission.
sigkdd#Best_Applications_Paper_Award: bestapplicationspaperaward is a child of award which is parented by beststudentpaperaward.
sigkdd#Award: bestapplicationspaperaward is the parent award of beststudentpaperaward and bestresearchpaperaward.
sigkdd#Deadline_Paper_Submission: The deadline paper submission is the child of the deadline abstractsubmission.
sigkdd#Deadline: The deadline for paper submission is the parent of deadlineabstractsubmission and deadlineauthornotification.
sigkdd#Deadline_Author_notification: The deadlineauthornotification is the child of the deadline and is the parent of the deadlineabstractsubmission.
sigkdd#Webmaster: The webmaster is a child of an organization which is child of a person.
sigkdd#Organizator: The webmaster and the generalchair are both parents of the organization which is also the parent of the organizingcommitteemember. The listener is a child of the organization which is also the parent of the generalchair and the programchair.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper_student: The author of paper is the child of the author who is the parent of the author.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Award: The beststudentpaperaward is the child of the award and the parent of the bestresearchpaperaward.
sigkdd#Author: The author is the child of the speaker, the invited speaker and the author of paper (student).
sigkdd#ACM_SIGKDD: acmsigkdd is a child of Thing.
sigkdd#Sponzor: Silversupporter and goldsupporter are both sponsors. They are also the parents of exhibitors and beststudentpapersupporter.
sigkdd#Exhibitor: The sponsor of the exhibitors is the parent of the beststudentpapersupporter.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGMOD_Member: sponzorfee is the parent of registrationfee which is the child of registrationsigmodmember.
sigkdd#Registration_fee: Registrationfee is the parent of registrationsigmodmember and registrationnonmember. It is also the child of registrationstudent and sponzorfee.
sigkdd#Person: The listener is the parent of the speaker, the author of paperstudent and the speaker is the parent of the programcommittee member. The child of the speaker is the child of the Thing.
sigkdd#Bronze_Supporter: The bronzesupporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the beststudentpapersupporter.
sigkdd#Committee: The committee is the parent of the programcommittee, the organizingcommittee and the bestpaperawardscommittee.
sigkdd#Platinum_Supporter: The sponsor of platinumsupporter is the parent of silversupporter.
sigkdd#Conference_hall: The conferencehall is the child of the mainoffice.
sigkdd#Best_Paper_Awards_Committee: The bestpaperawardscommittee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the organizingcommittee.
sigkdd#Program_Chair: The programchair is a child of the organization which is the parent of the programcommittee member.
sigkdd#Main_office: The main office is the child of the hotel.
sigkdd#Registration_Non-Member: registrationfee is a child of registrationfee which is a child of registrationfee.
sigkdd#Fee: sponzorfee and registrationfee are both parents of fee.
sigkdd#Review: Review is a child of document which is parented by paper.
sigkdd#Sponzor_fee: sponzorfee is child of fee which is parented by registrationfee and registrationsigmodmember.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGKDD_Member: The registrationsigkddmember is the child of registrationfee which is the parent of sponzorfee.
sigkdd#Program_Committee: The programcommittee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the organizingcommittee.
sigkdd#General_Chair: The generalchair is a child of an organization which is child of a person.
sigkdd#Speaker: The speaker is a child of a person who is the parent of the generalchair and the author of paper. He is also the parent of the invited speaker.
sigkdd#Gold_Supporter: goldsupporter is a child of sponsor who is the parent of beststudentpapersupporter.
sigkdd#Registration_Student: The registrationstudent is a child of the registrationfee which is a child of the fee.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee: The organizingcommittee is the child of the committee which is the parent of the bestpaperawardscommittee.
sigkdd#Listener: The listener is a child of the speaker and the author of paper. The author is the parent of the speaker.
sigkdd#Program_Committee_member: The programcommittee member is a child of the organization which is parented by the programchair.
sigkdd#Invited_Speaker: The invited speaker is the child of the speaker and the author is the parent of the author ofpaperstudent.
sigkdd#Best_Research_Paper_Award: bestresearchpaperaward is a child of award which is parented by bestapplicationspaperaward.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Supporter: beststudentpapersupporter is child of sponsor who is parent of silversupporter.
sigkdd#Paper: The paper is the child of the document which is the parent of the review.
sigkdd#Silver_Supporter: The silversupporter is the child of the sponsor who is the parent of the platinumsupporter.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee_member: The organizingcommitteemember is a child of the organization which is parented by the programcommitteemember.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper: The author of paper is the child of the author and the speaker. The speaker is the parent of the invited speaker.
